name: ACQUA DI GIOIA JASMINE
description: Exhilarating. Delicate. Acqua di Gioia's signature jasmine heart pulses with fresh, new energy. Its greenest facets are celebrated in a new and vital essence of joy. Green is the colour of nature, endlessly nuanced from verdant forests to cool waters, from tender greens, luminous after a summer rain, to the intense, fathomless greens of a restless sea, each vibrating with life.
